::Shredder/Kluster::

Shredder nods. "Allright then," he says, looking at the others, "Try 
not to cause too much trouble though."

He turns around to look at Kluster, who was frowning for some reason.

"What's going on?" Shredder asks.

"Nothing, I just recieved an interesting transmission. Well, lets 
go," Kluster turns around and sets off toward the bridge, Shredder 
following him. The Maximal's mind was flowing with questions. Deemos 
had allied with he Alliance and was now inviting them. Was it a trap? 
The Alliance didn't seem to have met with the Predacons for a while, 
perhaps they could help the Maximals in this.
